; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1119-1134: auto xact cost handling
; When an auto transaction matches a posting with total cost (@@),
; the auto-generated posting inherits the price annotation.
; Line 1126: amt.sign() < 0 triggers cost negation (in_place_negate)
; Line 1127: in_place_negate() on the cost

= /^Expenses/
    [Assets:Budget:$account]    -1.0
    [Assets:Checking]            1.0

2024/01/01 Utility Bill
    Expenses:Utilities    100 kWh @@ $72.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Utility Bill          Expenses:Utilities          100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Cash                    $-72         $-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                [A:Bu:Expen:Utilities]     -100 kWh         $-72
                                [Assets:Checking]           100 kWh         $-72
                                                                         100 kWh
end test
